Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.58,0:13:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The present state of the Earth\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}contradicts our records.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We demand explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Your speech is getting better and better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.01,0:13:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Translating everything must be tough. \NWhy don't you at least show us your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by\N "show us your face"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.59,0:13:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean you, the person inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.85,0:13:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nobody inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.87,0:13:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.36,0:13:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It really {\i1}is{\i0} empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.00,0:13:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I am an interface system that supports\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}and oversees the development of pilots.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.84,0:13:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A system?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:14:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a machine that's talking?
