Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Chamber is an AI that offers the pilot combat and survival support.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.08,0:14:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's really no one\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}inside! It's a machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.90,0:14:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I reiterate: Tell us about\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}the current state of the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{overlap}Oh my gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.68,0:14:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They say it used to be a planet of ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.57,0:14:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the ice melted, and it\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}became a planet of water.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Supposedly, long ago they had this place called "land" too,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm not sure what that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.89,0:14:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we live like this,\Nby connecting our ships into fleets.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.97,0:14:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still old ships and resources at the bottom of the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.89,0:14:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and we pull those back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.00,0:14:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Gargantia—oh, that's the name of this fleet—is no exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Gargantia?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.50,0:14:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Gargantia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.26,0:14:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there others?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.73,0:14:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.70,0:15:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's other fleets too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.62,0:15:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They come in all sizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.27,0:15:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All you need to do is chain\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}a couple ships together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.68,0:15:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There's also pesky ones, like pirates.
