Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.49,0:15:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Are these "pirates" the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, kinda.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.70,0:15:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a galaxy current.\N Some call it a "sea galaxy."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really pretty,\N so keep watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.86,0:15:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we'll get a\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}new galaxy current.{lit: that should result in a new galaxy current}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Define "galaxy current."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.36,0:15:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Shining currents on the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.78,0:15:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We can only live on those,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.11,0:15:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,so we sail on,\N following the currents,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.81,0:15:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but they don't go on forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually we need to find a new galaxy current to switch to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.40,0:16:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The sea galaxy shines\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}because of lightbugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.54,0:16:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They're tiny creatures\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}that store electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.83,0:16:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We get our power\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}from this strip of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.49,0:16:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so pretty!
