Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.44,0:16:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.23,0:16:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you ascertain our coordinates?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.54,0:16:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to atmospheric interference, the lack of information,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.23,0:16:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and the limits of optical analysis,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,continued observation is required to\N successfully determine our current position.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, it's true! {SPLIT}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.24,0:16:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not even {\i1}trying{\i0}\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}to make it sound realistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.46,0:16:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,In the small chance that indeed was a talking machine—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.76,0:17:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, waging war\N against space creatures?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a load of bull!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.61,0:17:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What we {\i1}should{\i0} do is take it apart\N and see for ourselves if it can really talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.24,0:17:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The kid can just sleep with the fishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.90,0:17:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They've got no place to go!\N They need help!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.25,0:17:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You should listen to\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}what Ledo's telling us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.13,0:17:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Extensive contact with the abnormal is profitable to no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.71,0:17:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This applies to both sea and space.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.62,0:17:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Location identified.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is definitely where\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}we found that Yunboro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then! Leave no stone unturned!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.07,0:17:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Supplies are plentiful here, and\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}the locals pose little to no threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Conditionally agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:18:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can't return to the\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}battlefront by ourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll just have to wait for our allies to notice our distress signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Building a cooperative relationship here is probably the best choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.63,0:18:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.84,0:18:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Words like "battlefront" and "allies" are completely foreign to the people of this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.81,0:18:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Our life-and-death struggle against\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}the Hideauze doesn't concern them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.99,0:18:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.60,0:18:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates are attacking the salvagers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.71,0:18:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Bellows' ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Bellows' people...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.73,0:18:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot! {SPLIT}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The cocky bastards are attacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.08,0:18:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Guard Captain!{護衛長?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.25,0:18:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No chance! There's too many of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.92,0:18:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Salvagers, stay underwater!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.72,0:19:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Multiple engine sounds detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirm it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.01,0:19:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ledo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.68,0:19:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.73,0:19:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They have kites?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They have nine ships\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}and several small boats.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.47,0:19:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They are attacking with kites.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the reinforcements?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.70,0:19:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They might not make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,An enemy attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you guys strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.88,0:19:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that a super-strong Yunboro?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.88,0:19:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Help us! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.97,0:19:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,She requests assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.98,0:19:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it. We can use it\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}as a bargaining chip later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:19:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Activate floater.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The weird Yunboro's moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.72,0:20:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're Bellows of Gargantia?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Take what you can and get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.06,0:20:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you sticking\N with this shitty fleet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.96,0:20:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.18,0:20:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Rackage thinks very highly of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.16,0:20:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Dream on, pathetic pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.89,0:20:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.08,0:21:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better not try to piss us off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.67,0:21:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.13,0:21:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Friend-or-foe identification\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}of the larger units complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Requesting permission\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}to identify smaller targets.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.53,0:21:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Identification complete.
